# Raw terrain source scans are local/heavy inputs. Commit only text metadata and
# reproduce the sources through the locked acquisition scripts.
assets-source/terrain/**
!assets-source/terrain/README.md
!assets-source/terrain/.gitkeep

# Runtime terrain maps are deterministic build products. CI publishes them as an
# artifact and Vite/production builds regenerate them through predev/prebuild.
public/assets/terrain/generated/**
